Uses https://github.com/fridgerator/PyNode.

* Create and activate Python virtualenv (or use the same one as installed for the regular IRC version)
* Install gyp-next (or perhaps plain gyp): git clone https://github.com/nodejs/gyp-next; cd gyp-next; pip install -e .
* npm install @fridgerator/pynode
* `node testjs.js` should print "success!"

